we don't get to give him at
least. like. a little memorial service.

8
00:01:11.113 --> 00:01:12.340
I know.

9
00:01:12.364 --> 00:01:14.467
I just wish we could
honor him. you know?

10
00:01:14.491 --> 00:01:16.159
