15
00:01:31.633 --> 00:01:32.759
Do you think…

16
00:01:34.511 --> 00:01:36.180
That he's still. like…

17
00:01:41.393 --> 00:01:44.730
I mean. do you believe
in… you know. like…

18
00:01:46.523 --> 00:01:47.858
- Heaven?
- Yeah.

19
00:01:50.110 --> 00:01:51.111
You know.

20
00:01:52.196 --> 00:01:55.675
I don't think there's some
magical place in the clouds

21
00:01:55.699 --> 00:01:57.201
where all the ghosts hang out.

22
00:01:57.951 --> 00:01:58.952
All right.

23
00:02:01.914 --> 00:02:03.332
But I really do think that

24
